cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a new framework for generative models using adversarial networks. The paper also includes experiments on image generation tasks, which are commonly studied in the computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of multiple discriminators also suggests a potential connection to neural networks (cs.NE) and the study of graph structures (cs.GR).
